# Secrets — must never enter a build context, let alone an image layer.
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/service-account.json

# Installed/derived artifacts: the image resolves its own from the lockfile.
**/node_modules
**/dist
.yarn/cache
.yarn/unplugged
.yarn/install-state.gz
.pnp.*

# Test + tooling output
**/coverage
**/test-results
**/playwright-report
**/blob-report
**/.vite

# Repo metadata irrelevant to the runtime
.git
.github
.husky
.history
**/*.md
!README.md
